seniors%20and%20mobility-impaired%20cats.%20The%20second%20entry%20also%20allows%20for%20a%20quick%20escape%20in%20households%20with%20multiple%20pets.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHeavy%20or%20large%20breed%20cats%20may%20have%20difficulty%20using%20many%20top-entry%20boxes.%20%26quot%3BA%20young%20adult%20cat%20that%20is%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fhow-heavy-should-my-cat-be%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eoverweight%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20should%20be%20able%20to%20use%20a%20top-entry%20litter%20box%2C%20and%20yes%2C%20the%20increased%20work%20required%20to%20use%20it%20might%20help%20with%20weight%20loss%2C%26quot%3B%20Freeman%20says.%20However%2C%20some%20top-entry%20boxes%20may%20still%20be%20too%20small%20or%20too%20challenging%20to%20access%20for%20large%20cats%20to%20use%20comfortably.%20Freeman%20recommends%20a%20low-entry%20box%20for%20senior%20cats%20who%20are%20overweight%20since%20these%20boxes%20may%20be%20easier%20on%20arthritic%20joints.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20box%20comes%20with%20a%20perforated%20folding%20top%20lid%20for%20easy%20cleaning%2C%20a%20walk-off%20platform%20to%20assist%20stepping%20in%20and%20out%2C%20two%20rip-resistant%20reusable%20plastic%20liners%2C%20and%20a%20scoop.%20It's%20made%20of%20sturdy%20injection-molded%20ABS%20plastic%20and%20comes%20in%20white%2C%20black%2C%20and%20gray.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2246c6c36c-820c-458c-bcb3-f8343cc32217%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20budget%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EBest%20budget%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20you're%20unsure%20whether%20your%20cat%20will%20use%20a%20top-entry%20litter%20box%2C%20the%20Petmate%20Top%20Entry%20Litter%20Box%20is%20an%20affordable%20way%20to%20find%20out.%20Plus%2C%20since%20you'll%20need%20one%20more%20litter%20box%20than%20the%20number%20of%20cats%20in%20your%20home%2C%20it's%20reasonable%20to%20start