0litter%20box%20furniture%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20doesn't%20just%20provide%20cats%20with%20a%20secure%20and%20private%20space%20to%20do%20their%20business.%20It%20also%20provides%20their%20human%20counterparts%20with%20an%20inconspicuous%20piece%20of%20furniture%20that%20completely%20hides%20the%20cat's%20toilet.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Qlevo%20box%20is%20designed%20to%20accommodate%20a%20large%20litter%20box%20and%20make%20cleaning%20a%20breeze.%20The%20perforated%20entry%20and%20exit%20platform%20provides%20ventilation%20and%20helps%20reduce%20litter%20tracking.%20Plus%2C%20the%20no-slam%20hydraulic%20hinges%20that%20keep%20the%20top%20lid%20propped%20open%20simplify%20scooping%20and%20cleaning.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20this%20litter%20box%20enclosure%20is%20generously%20sized%2C%20the%20brand%20can%20also%20accommodate%20custom%20size%20requests.%20The%2048-pound%20enclosure%20comes%20fully%20assembled.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221198238d-f0f7-4a84-b45a-fea89c79e71f%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20self-cleaning%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EBest%20self-cleaning%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFinding%20the%20right%20litter%20box%20setup%20may%20take%20some%20trial%20and%20error.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20determining%20what%20will%20work%20best%20for%20a%20specific%20cat%2C%20it's%20a%20good%20idea%20to%20offer%20at%20least%20two%20different%20types%20of%20litter%2C%20experimenting%20with%20various%20substrates%20until%20you%20find%20one%20the%20cat%20will%20use%20consistently%2C%26quot%3B%20Freeman%20says.%20Your%20options%20for%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-cat-litter%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ebest%20cat%20litters%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20vary%20widely%2C%20from%20clumping%20clay%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-natural-cat-litter%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ebest%20natural%20cat%20litter%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20made%20of%20corn%2C%20walnut%2C%20wood%2C%20or%20grass.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20top-entry%20box%20uses%20crystal%20cat%20litter%20made%20of%20non-clumping%20silica%20crystals%20that%20quickly%20absorb%20liquids%20and%20neutralize%20odors.%20Just%2020%20minutes%20after%20your%20cat%20leaves%20the%20litter%20box%2C%20the%20automated%20rake%20will%20sift%20solid%20waste%20into%20a%20covered%20waste%20trap.%20The%20brand%20says%20you'll%20need%20to%20replace%20the%20disposable%20crystal%20litter%20tray%20with%20a%20fresh%20refill%20once%20a%20month%20for%20single-cat%20households.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20entry%20hood%20is%20made%20of%20semi-transparent%20plastic%2C%20so%20your%20cat%20will%20have%20plenty%20of%20visibility%20to%20spot%20an%20approaching%20furry%20family%20member.%20You%20can%20also%20completely%20remove%20the%20entry%20hood%20by%20snapping%20it%20in%20and%20out%20of%20place%2C%20if%20it%20turns%20out%20your%20cat%20doesn't%20want%20to%20use%20a%20top-entry%20box%20at%20all.%20The%20ScoopFree%20box%20also%20has%20a%20built-in%20smart%20counter%20to%20let%20you%20know%20how%20many%20times%20a%20day%20your%20cat%20uses%20the%20box%20and%20when%20you%20should%20refresh%20the%20litter.%20Reviewers%20recommend%20changing%20it%20after%20about%20every%2050%20uses.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22197b66ae-f28c-4b5f-b121-902745c93ff1%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20for%20corners%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EBest%20for%20corners%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKrebsbach%20says%20cats%20value%20their%20privacy%20while%20using%20the%20litter%20box.%20She%20says%20that%20a%20top-entry%20litter%20box%20can%20provide%20extra%20privacy%2C%20but%20placing%20a%20litter%20box%20in%20a%20low-traffic%20area%20is%20even%20better.%20Of%20course%2C%20finding%20a%20discreet%20spot%20for%20your%20cat's%20litter%20box%20can%20prove%20somewhat%20challenging%20when%20you%20share%20a%20small%20home%20or%20apartment%20with%20cats.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThanks%20to%20its%20triangular%20design%2C%20the%20Kitangle%20top-entry%20corner%20litter%20box%20fits%20perfectly%20into%20unused%2C%20low-traffic%20corner%20spaces.%20Made%20of%20sturdy%20polypropylene%20plastic%2C%20it%20has%20a%20seamless%2C%20roomy%20design.%20The%20removable%20lid%20simplifies%20cleaning%20and%20the%20brand%20says%20there's%20no%20need%20for%20a%20litter%20liner%20in%20this%20box.%20Just%20add%20your%20cat's%20preferred%20type%20of%20litter%2C%20and%20it's%20ready%20to%20use.%20The%20litter%20box%20weighs%20about%209%20pounds%20and%20doesn't%20require%20assembly.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2215b1442a-9daf-499f-84ef-4b20ffda16c7%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20luxury%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EBest%20luxury%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECats%20need%20a%20clean%20litter%20box%20that%20offers%20a%20secure%20and%20private%20place%20to%20do%20their%20business.%20We%20humans%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20would%20rather%20have%20a%20box%20that%20doesn't%20show%20off%20its%20contents%20and%20can%20blend%20in%20with%20home%20d%C3%A9cor.%20Omlet's%20Enclosed%20Cat%20Litter%20Box%20with%20Storage%2C%20then%2C%20might%20offer%20the%20perfect%20solution.%20This%20top-entry%20cabinet%20has%20plenty%20of%20space%20for%20your%20cat.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20design%20features%20an%20anti-tracking%20platform%20that%20minimizes%20litter%20tracking.%20The%20Omlet%20litter%20box%20includes%20a%20reusable%20litter%20liner%2C%20a%20folding%20litter%20box%20scoop%2C%20and%20an%20activated%20carbon%20filter%20designed%20to%20absorb%20and%20trap%20offensive%20odors.%20You%20can%20lift%20and%20fold%20back%20the%20anti-tracking%20platform%20for%20easy%20scooping.%20When%20it's%20time%20for%20a%20deep%20clean%2C%20just%20slide%20out%20the%20platform%20and%20unsnap%20the%20anti-slip%20retention%20band%20to%20remove%20the%20litter%20liner.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ab5b564e-2456-484f-a54b-eca842d4f57d%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20to%20look%20for%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20a%20top-entry%20litter%20box%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBased%20on%20our%20experts'%20insights%2C%20thorough%20research%2C%20and%20personal%20experience%2C%20we%20identified%20the%20following%20key%20features%20to%20look%20for%20when%20shopping%20for%20one%20of%20the%20best%20top-entry%20litter%20boxes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ESize%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIf%20your%20cat%20can't%20easily%20stand%20up%20and%20turn%20around%20in%20their%20box%2C%20they%20may%20find%20another%20place%20to%20eliminate.%20We%20considered%20litter%20boxes%20designed%20for%20cats%20of%20all%20sizes%2C%20along%20with%20boxes%20that%20fit%20well%20in%20both%20small%20and%20large%20spaces.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EAccessibility%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Accessibility%20was%20a%20crucial%20factor%20we%20considered%20when%20choosing%20the%20best%20litter%20boxes.%20While%20some%20cats%20can%20use%20top-entry%20boxes%20comfortably%2C%20large%20breeds%2C%20overweight%20cats%2C%20senior%20cats%2C%20and%20cats%20with%20mobility%20issues%20may%20find%20them%20more%20challenging.%20We%20chose%20top-entry%20boxes%20designed%20to%20accommodate%20cats%20of%20all%20sizes%20and%20weights%2C%20including%20boxes%20with%20additional%20options%20for%20entry%20and%20exit.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EEase%20of%20assembly%20and%20cleaning%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20chose%20top-entry%20litter%20boxes%20that%20come%20fully%20assembled%20or%20have%20straightforward%20assembly%20instructions.%20We%20also%20looked%20for%20easy-clean%2C%20user-friendly%20designs%20that%20help%20minimize%20litter%20tracking%20in%20your%20home.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224741469f-94a1-45c3-abbc-45a66ec893c1%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20selected%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EHow%20we%20selected%20the%20best%20top-entry%20litter%20boxes%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20this%20guide%2C%20we%20consulted%20two%20veterinarians%20and%20a%20certified%20feline%20training%20and%20behavior%20specialist%20to%20select%20the%20best%20top-entry%20litter%20boxes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDr.%20Susan%20Krebsbach%20is%20a%20veterinarian%20and%20practice%20owner%20of%20Creature%20Counseling.%20Krebsbach%20helped%20us%20understand%20the%20importance%20of%20litter%20box%20placement%20and%20selection.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDr.%20Mark%20Freeman%20is%20a%20board-certified%20veterinarian%20and%20assistant%20professor%20of%20community%20practice%20at%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvetmed.vt.edu%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EVirginia-Maryland%20College%20of%20Veterinary%20Medicine%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Freeman%20helped%20us%20understand%20the%20special%20needs%20of%20overweight%20and%20senior%20cats%20and%20the%20lifestyle%20accommodations%20they%20may%20require.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMolly%20DeVoss%20is%20a%20certified%20feline%20training%20and%20behavior%20specialist%20(CFTBS)%2C%20certified%20cat%20behavior%20consultant%2C%20and%20Fear%20Free%20certified%20trainer%20who%20specializes%20in%20using%20positive%20reinforcement%20to%20modify%20and%20prevent%20unwanted%20behaviors%20in%20cats.%20She%20is%20the%20founder%20and%20owner%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.catbehaviorsolutions.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ECat%20Behavior%20Solutions%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20DeVoss%20helped%20us%20understand%20the%20basic%20litter%20box%20requirements%20for%20cats.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20considered%20both%20expert%20input%20and%20our%20previous%20testing%20and%20experience%20with%20top-entry%20litter%20pans.%20We%20conducted%20thorough%20research%20to%20establish%20our%20selection%20criteria%20for%20the%20litter%20boxes%20and%20excluded%20any%20products%20with%20a%20history%20of%20negative%20reviews.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22164f0448-a4dc-46ec-86a1-58edf76ca76e%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22FAQs%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ETop-entry%20litter%20box%20FAQs%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3EDo%20cats%20like%20top-entry%20litter%20boxes%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ECertain%20cats%20may%20favor%20top-entry%20boxes%20for%20increased%20privacy%2C%20particularly%20those%20who%20enjoy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fwhy-do-cats-like-boxes%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehiding%20in%20enclosed%20areas%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20who%20live%20with%20a%20curious%20canine.%20Features%20like%20multiple%20entryways%2C%20slots%20for%20light%20and%20ventilation%2C%20grates%2C%20and%20semi-transparent%20walls%20can%20add%20visibility%2C%20helping%20cats%20feel%20more%20at%20ease%20while%20using%20an%20enclosed%20litter%20box.%20However%2C%20less%20confident%20cats%20or%20those%20who%20have%20conflicts%20with%20other%20pets%20may%20prefer%20an%20open%20litter%20box.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EAre%20top-entry%20litter%20boxes%20OK%20for%20cats%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ETop-entry%20boxes%20are%20OK%20for%20cats%20to%20use%2C%20though%20they%20may%20benefit%20you%20more%20than%20your%20cat.%20Freeman%20says%20top-entry%20boxes%20can%20help%20reduce%20litter%20box%20messes%20and%20the%20amount%20of%20litter%20cats%20track%20outside%20the%20box.%20They%20also%20limit%20a%20dog's%20access%20to%20the%20litter%20box.%20However%2C%20the%20best%20top-entry%20boxes%20don't%20offer%20many%20advantages%20to%20cats%2C%20except%20for%20helping%20select%20cats%20feel%20more%20secure.%20Our%20experts%20advise%20against%20using%20top-entry%20boxes%20for%20senior%20or%20overweight%20cats%20with%20arthritis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20is%20the%20point%20of%20a%20top-entry%20litter%20box%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20top-entry%20litter%20boxes%20can%20reduce%20litter%20spills%2C%20litter%20tracking%2C%20and%20the%20possibility%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fcat-spraying%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecats%20spraying%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20the%20edge%20of%20the%20litter%20box%20wall.%20Additionally%2C%20they%20limit%20a%20dog's%20access%20to%20the%20litter%20box.%20Certain%20cats%20may%20also%20like%20the%20privacy%20of%20a%20top-entry%20box.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EDo%20cats%20prefer%20open%20or%20hooded%20litter%20boxes%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EDeVoss%20explains%20that%20in%20the%20wild%2C%20cats%20prefer%20to%20eliminate%20in%20the%20open%20so%20they%20can%20keep%20track%20of%20potential%20threats.%20That's%20why%20most%20cats%20prefer%20an%20uncovered%20litter%20box%2C%20she%20says.%20You%20can%20help%20your%20cat%20feel%20more%20comfortable%20in%20an%20enclosed%20litter%20box%20by%20choosing%20one%20with%20multiple%20entryways%2C%20slots%2C%20grates%2C%20and%20semi-transparent%20walls.%20Cats%20have%20specific%20preferences%20for%20their%20litter%20box%2C%20and%20an%20aversion%20to%20the%20box%20can%20cause%20issues%20with%20inappropriate%20elimination.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20do%20you%20train%20a%20cat%20to%20use%20a%20top-entry%20litter%20box%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EPositive%20reinforcement%2C%20which%20involves%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fhow-to-train-your-cat%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epraising%20your%20cat%20for%20a%20behavior%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20is%20an%20effective%20way%20to%20encourage%20desired%20behaviors%20in%20cats.%20However%2C%20DeVoss%20cautions%20against%20using%20positive%20reinforcement%20to%20encourage%20your%20cat%20to%20do%20something%20that%20goes%20against%20their%20natural%20tendencies%20%E2%80%94%20like%20using%20a%20covered%20litter%20box%20if%20it%20causes%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-tell-if-your-dog-cat-is-stressed-what-to-do%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estress%3C%2Fa%3E.%20If%20your%20cat%20avoids%20the%20litter%20box%20or%20eliminates%20outside%20of%20it%20consistently%2C%20they%20may%20find%20it%20too%20stressful%20to%20use%2C%20and%20no%20amount%20of%20praise%20may%20make%20a%20difference.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20most%20cats%20can%20adjust%20to%20using%20a%20top-entry%20box.%20To%20encourage%20a%20cat%20to%20use%20a%20new%20litter%20box%2C%20place%20it%20next%20to%20their%20existing%20one%2C%20giving%20them%20the%20choice%20to%20switch.%20When%20the%20cat%20consistently%20uses%20the%20new%20litter%20box%2C%20remove%20the%20old%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EAre%20top-entry%20litter%20boxes%20good%20for%20small%20spaces%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ETop-entry%20boxes%20are%20a%20good%20option%20for%20small%20living%20spaces%2C%20since%20they%20can%20help%20minimize%20litter%20tracking%20and%20odors.%20They%20also%20limit%20a%20dog's%20entry%20to%20your%20cat's%20litter%20box%2C%20so%20they%20may%20work%20well%20in%20households%20with%20both%20cats%20and%20dogs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3ECan%20kittens%20use%20a%20top-entry%20box%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ETop-entry%20boxes%20may%20not%20be%20suitable%20for%20very%20young%20kittens%20because%20they%20lack%20the%20strength%20and%20dexterity%20to%20access%20the%20entry%2C%20Freeman%20says.%20The%20boxes%20may%20work%20best%20for%20cats%20between%20the%20ages%20of%205%20months%20old%20and%208%20years%20old%2C%20though%20they%20may%20also%20work%20for%20older%20cats%20with%20no%20mobility%20issues.%20However%2C%20Freeman%20cautions%20that%20osteoarthritis%20is%20common%20in%20older%20cats%20and%20significantly%20underdiagnosed.%20Cats%20who%20experience%20pain%20and%20limited%20mobility%20due%20to%20osteoarthritis%20may%20find%20it%20difficult%20or%20impossible%20to%20use%20a%20top-entry%20box.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3