%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20states%20that%20the%20policy%20applies%20to%20all%20Amazon%20employees%20in%20Germany%2C%20but%20it%20does%20not%20include%20Twitch%20and%20Audible%20employees.%20It%20added%20that%20Amazon%20could%20reconsider%20or%20change%20informal%20arrangements%20%26quot%3Bat%20its%20discretion%20at%20any%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20measure%20includes%20two%20types%20of%20work%20arrangements%3A%20informal%20and%20formal.%20Under%20the%20formal%20arrangement%2C%20employees%20can%20request%20to%20work%20from%20home%20for%20up%20to%20two%20days%20a%20week%20and%20change%20their%20scheduled%20hours%2C%20per%20the%20document.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20an%20informal%20basis%2C%20managers%20can%20approve%20ad%20hoc%20requests%20made%20with%2024%20hours'%20notice%20to%20work%20from%20home%2C%20the%20document%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20added%20that%20formal%20flexible%20working%20arrangements%20change%20employee%20contractual%20terms%20and%20conditions%20and%20%26quot%3Brequire%20documentation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20document%20also%20said%20that%20Amazon%20will%20take%20disciplinary%20action%2C%20including%20terminating%20employment%2C%20for%20staff%20who%20fail%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnnouncing%20the%20five-day%20RTO%20mandate%20in%20September%2C%20Jassy%20said%20he%20wanted%20Amazon%20to%20%26quot%3Boperate%20like%20the%20world's%20largest%20startup.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BThat%20means%20having%20a%20passion%20for%20constantly%20inventing%20for%20customers%2C%20strong%20urgency%20(for%20most%20big%20opportunities%2C%20it's%20a%20race!)%2C%20high%20ownership%2C%20fast%20decision-making%2C%20scrappiness%20and%20frugality%2C%20deeply%20connected%20collaboration%20(you%20need%20to%20be%20joined%20at%20the%20hip%20with%20your%20teammates%20when%20inventing%20and%20solving%20hard%20problems)%2C%20and%20a%20shared%20commitment%20to%20each%20other.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20said%20in%20June%20that%20it's%20on%20track%20to%20have%20more%20than%2040%2C000%20permanent%20employees%20in%20Germany%20by%20the%20end%20of%20this%20year.%20It%20also%20announced%20an%20investment%20of%20%E2%82%AC10%20billion%20(about%20%2410.4%20billion)%20in%20the%20country%20to%20expand%20its%20logistics%20network%20and%20cloud%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20a%20tech%20worker%20with%20insights%20to%20share%3F%20Contact%20the%20reporter%2C%20Jyoti%20Mann%2C%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ajmann%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3Ejmann%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20%3Cem%3Eor%20Signal%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3Ejyotimann.11%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EReach%20out%20via%20a%20nonwork%20device%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-germany-office-return-flexible-policy-rto-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732296334000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6740838e9f2901eb603650a3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-germany-office-return-flexible-policy-rto-2024-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20Amazon%20internal%20policy%2C%20seen%20by%20BI%2C%20outlines%20how%20staff%20in%20Germany%20can%20apply%20to%20work%20from%20home%20once%20a%20week%2C%20or%20twice%20in%20exceptional%20circumstances.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jmann%40insider.com%20(Jyoti%20Mann)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-germany-office-return-flexible-policy-rto-2024-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kendrick%20Lamar%20Drops%20%E2%80%98GNX%E2%80%99%3A%20New%20Album%20Features%20SZA%2C%20Jack%20Antonoff%2C%20Kamasi%20Washingto