photo%2Fmsid-115570119%2Cimgsize-50248.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fwhen-arjun-kapoor-talked-about-completing-a-decade-in-bollywood-and-his-protective-big-brother-persona%2Farticleshow%2F115570119.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F115570119.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EIn%20a%20recent%20interview%2C%20Arjun%20Kapoor%20reflected%20on%20his%20school%20days%2C%20where%20he%20played%20the%20role%20of%20a%20protective%20older%20brother%20to%20his%20cousins%2C%20Sonam%20and%20Rhea%20Kapoor.%20He%20emphasized%20the%20significance%20of%20his%20bond%20with%20his%20sisters%2C%20particularly%20in%20navigating%20the%20dynamics%20of%20his%20parents'%20separation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fwhen-arjun-kapoor-talked-about-completing-a-decade-in-bollywood-and-his-protective-big-brother-persona%2Farticleshow%2F115570119.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'No%20Power%20Deals%20With%20Adani%20Group'%3A%20BJD%2C%20DMK%20Reject%20US%20Charge%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20allegations%20that%20Odisha%20government%20officials%20took%20bribes%20for%20a%20power%20purchase%20agreement%20in%202021%2C%20when%20it%20was%20in%20power%20in%20the%20state%2C%20the%20Naveen%20Patnaik-led%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%20has%20said%20the%20deal%20was%20between%20two%20government%20entities%20and%20no%20private%20parties%2C%20including%20the%20Adani%20Group%2C%20were%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20similar%20statement%20has%20also%20been%20made%20by%20the%20DMK%2C%20which%20is%20in%20power%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20power%20purchase%20agreement%20made%20in%202021%20was%20between%20two%20government%20agencies%20-%20a%20central%20government%20public%20sector%20undertaking%20(PSU)%20which%20is%20a%20mini%20navratna%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20Solar%20Energy%20Corporation%20of%20India%20(under%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Renewable%20Energy)%20and%20a%20state%20govt%20PSU%20Gridco%20-%20solely%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20supply%20of%20renewable%20energy.%20This%20is%20part%20of%20a%20central%20government%20scheme%20called%20the%20manufacturing%20linked%20solar%20scheme%2C%26quot%3B%20Pratap%20Keshari%20Deb%2C%20Odisha's%20former%20energy%20minister%20and%20the%20deputy%20chief%20whip%20of%20the%20BJD%20in%20the%20state%20Assembly%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Deb%20said%20that%20the%20agreement%20was%20to%20procure%20500%20MW%20of%20renewable%20energy%20from%20the%20Solar%20Energy%20Corporation%20of%20India%20(SECI)%20at%20the%20lowest%20rates%20discovered%20by%20the%20PSU.%20%26quot%3BThere%20was%20no%20engagement%20with%20any%20private%20party%20whatsoever%2C%20including%20the%20Adani%20Group%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20that%20the%20state%20has%20been%20procuring%20renewable%20energy%20from%20central%20government%20PSUs%20like%20SECI%20and%20the%20National%20Thermal%20Power%20Corporation%20(NTPC)%20since%202011%2C%20the%20party%20said%20that%20the%20allegations%20were%20%26quot%3Bbaseless%20and%20incorrect%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETamil%20Nadu%20Electricity%20Minister%20V%20Senthil%20Balaji%20said%20the%20state%20has%20an%20understanding%20to%20buy%20power%20only%20from%20a%20firm%20owned%20by%20the%20Union%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20like%20to%20first%20clarify%20that%20as%20regards%20TN%20Generation%20and%20Distribution%20Corporation%20(TANGEDCO)%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20kind%20of%20commercial%20relationship%20with%20Mr%20Adani's%20company%20during%20the%20past%20three%20years%20(after%20the%20DMK%20formed%20the%20government%20in%20May%202021)%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Balaji%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20said%20Tamil%20Nadu%20inked%20a%20pact%20for%20procurement%20of%201%2C500MW%20with%20SECI%2C%20adding%20%26quot%3Bthere%20is%20no%20direct%20contact%20with%20Mr%20Adani's%20firm%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Adani%20Group%20has%20firmly%20denied%20a%20US%20government%20department%20report%20alleging%20bribery%20for%20power%20contracts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20possible%20legal%20recourse%20will%20be%20sought.%20The%20Adani%20Group%20has%20always%20upheld%20and%20is%20steadfastly%20committed%20to%20maintaining%20the%20highest%20standards%20of%20governance%2C%20transparency%20and%20regulatory%20compliance%20across%20all%20jurisdictions%20of%20its%20operations.%20We%20assure%20our%20stakeholders%2C%20partners%20and%20employees%20that%20we%20are%20a%20law-abiding%20organisation%2C%20fully%20compliant%20with%20all%20laws%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Group%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Disclaimer%3A%20New%20Delhi%20Television%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20AMG%20Media%20Networks%20Limited%2C%20an%20Adani%20Group%20Company.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732288920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fmjb5lrag_pratap-keshari-deb-bjd_625x300_22_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fodisha-had-no-dealings-with-adani-group-bjd-rejects-us-charge-7080988%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Responding%20to%20allegations%20that%20Odisha%20government%20officials%20took%20bribes%20for%20a%20power%20purchase%20agreement%20in%202021%2C%20when%20it%20was%20in%20power%20in%20the%20state%2C%20the%20Naveen%20Patnaik-led%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%20has%20said%20the%20deal%20was%20between%20two%20government%20entities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fodisha-