20rebuilt%20with%20the%20help%20of%20hundreds%20of%20specialist%20artisans%20and%20millions%20of%20donations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNotre-Dame%20has%20been%20restored%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20said%20on%20X%2C%20as%20he%20shared%20a%2094-minute%20clip%20of%20the%20renovated%20cathedral%20that%20is%20set%20to%20reopen%20on%20December%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ENotre-Dame%20has%20been%20restored!%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fg7RKQDHRlr%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fg7RKQDHRlr%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Elon%20Musk%20(%40elonmusk)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1859593835535331439%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2021%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20report%20by%20the%20National%20Geographic%20said%20everything%20has%20been%20spruced%20up%20-%20the%20frescoes%2C%20checked%20floor%20and%20the%20bells%20-%20which%20have%20been%20removed%20from%20the%20belfry%2C%20cleaned%20of%20lead%20dust%2C%20and%20restored%20at%20the%20Norman%20foundry%20where%20they%20were%20first%20cast%20-%20among%20others.%20A%20high-tech%20new%20lighting%20system%20will%20also%20contribute%20to%20the%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Forbes%2C%20the%20renovation%20was%20carried%20out%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20around%20500%20million%20euros.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20surplus%20of%20about%20140%20million%20euros%20will%20be%20used%20for%20future%20preservation%20work%20on%20the%20861-year-old%20building%2C%26quot%3B%20Philippe%20Jost%2C%20who%20has%20overseen%20the%20project%2C%20told%20Forbes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20AFP%20report%20said%20before%20the%20fire%2C%20Notre-Dame%20was%20among%20the%20most%20visited%20buildings%20in%20Europe%2C%20with%2014%20to%2015%20million%20a%20year%20expected%20to%20visit%20once%20the%20cathedral%20reopens%20next%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20April%2015%2C%202019%2C%20a%20fire%20broke%20out%20in%20the%20attic%2C%20beneath%20the%20cathedral's%20roof%2C%20causing%20severe%20damages%20to%20the%20wooden%20spire%2C%20which%20had%20collapsed%2C%20and%20the%20wooden%20roof%2C%20besides%20the%20cathedral's%20upper%20walls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20works%20of%20art%20and%20religious%20relics%20were%20moved%20to%20safety%20but%20others%20suffered%20smoke%20damage.%20Some%20of%20the%20exterior%20art%20was%20also%20damaged%20or%20destroyed%20in%20the%20blaze.%20At%20least%20two%20police%20officers%20and%20one%20firefighter%20were%20injured%20as%20around%20400%20firefighters%20worked%20through%20the%20night%2C%20taking%20roughly%20around%20nine%20hours%20to%20extinguish%20the%20blaze.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20European%20Commission%20(a%20politically%20independent%20executive%20arm%20of%20the%20European%20Union)%2C%20a%20large%20part%20of%20the%20cathedral%20roof%20and%20spire%20were%20made%20of%20lead%2C%20and%20some%20studies%20suggested%20that%20150%20kg%20of%20lead%20was%20spread%20during%20the%20fire.%20Others%20hinted%20that%20one%20tonne%20of%20lead%20must%20have%20fallen%20within%20one%20kilometre%20of%20the%20cathedral.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20exact%20cause%20of%20the%20fire%20could%20not%20be%20determined%20but%20French%20authorities%20claimed%20an%20electrical%20fault%20or%20a%20cigarette%20may%20have%20been%20responsible%20for%20the%20fire%2C%20according%20to%20Reuters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotre-Dame%20did%20not%20hold%20a%20Christmas%20mass%20in%202019%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%20since%201803.%20French%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20had%20announced%20a%20five-year%20plan%20to%20rebuild%20what%20was%20lost.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732281660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Figee9dfo_notre-dame-restoration_625x300_22_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-n