lling%20to%20bet%20on%20a%20%E2%80%98yes'%20for%20that%20one%2C%20anytime%20soon%3F%20Only%20some%20very%20optimistic%20people%20in%20Pakistan%20and%20the%20ICC%2C%20perhaps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20we%20venture%20further%20into%20the%20geo-political%20quagmire%20that%20the%20governing%20body%20of%20world%20cricket%20finds%20itself%20in%20currently%2C%20thanks%20to%20India's%20refusal%20to%20travel%20to%20Pakistan%20to%20play%20the%202025%20ICC%20Champions%20Trophy%20and%20Pakistan's%20belligerent%20refusal%20to%20accept%20a%20hybrid%20model%20this%20time%2C%20let's%20get%20a%20few%20things%20straight%20and%2C%20therefore%2C%20out%20of%20the%20way%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDespite%20Indian%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S.%20Jaishankar's%20recent%20visit%20to%20Pakistan%20to%20attend%20a%20conclave%2C%20there%20hasn't%20been%20a%20thaw%20in%20the%20relations%20between%20the%20two%20countries%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIndia%20haven't%20travelled%20to%20Pakistan%20to%20play%20cricket%20since%20the%202008%20Asia%20Cup%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20reason%20India%20stopped%20playing%20cricket%20in%20Pakistan%20and%20cut%20off%20many%20more%20ties%20was%20the%2026%2F11%20terror%20attacks%20in%20Mumbai%20in%202008%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIf%20the%20Pakistan%20camp%20thought%20that%20their%20travelling%20to%20India%20to%20play%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20last%20year%20was%20a%20gesture%20that%20would%20be%20reciprocated%20by%20India%20for%20next%20year's%20Champions%20Trophy%2C%20they%20were%20mistaken%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAnd%20finally%2C%20if%20India%20are%20to%20participate%20in%20an%20ICC%20tournament%20where%20Pakistan%20are%20hosts%2C%20their%20matches%20will%20have%20to%20be%20played%20at%20a%20neutral%20venue.%20And%20that%20will%20mostly%20be%20up%20to%20the%20ICC%20and%20the%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20to%20work%20out%20in%20order%20to%20avoid%20any%20potential%20heartburn.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20read%20the%20above%20and%20nodded%20your%20head%20in%20agreement%2C%20then%20you%20clearly%20think%20differently%20than%20people%20who%20govern%20world%20cricket%20but%20who%20seem%20to%20have%20forgotten%20the%20basics%20of%20current%20Indo-Pak%20cricketing%20relations.%20Strange%2C%20isn't%20it%3F%20After%20all%2C%20it%20was%20just%20last%20year%20when%20Pakistan%20hosted%20the%20Asia%20Cup.%20Back%20then%2C%20all%20of%20India's%20matches%2C%20including%20the%20final%2C%20were%20played%20in%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20as%20part%20of%20a%20hybrid%20model.%20It%20was%20a%20model%20that%20was%20proposed%20by%20the%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20(PCB)%20itself%20(after%20an%20impasse%2C%20of%20course)%20so%20that%20they%20could%20retain%20hosting%20rights.%20It%20was%20the%20right%20decision%20for%20everyone%20involved.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia%20Can't%20Be%20Ignored%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20crystal%20ball%20that%20can%20show%20us%20what%20lies%20ahead%2C%20but%20eventually%2C%20this%20is%20most%20likely%20going%20to%20be%20the%20solution%20for%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20next%20year%20as%20well.%20There%20are%20enough%20media%20reports%20indicating%20that%20back-channel%20talks%20are%20on%20between%20the%20ICC%20and%20the%20PCB%20to%20convince%20the%20Pakistan%20camp%20to%20agree%20to%20organise%20India's%20matches%20in%20the%20UAE.%20The%20other%20alternative%20is%20playing%20the%20tournament%20without%20India.%20But%20let's%20face%20it%2C%20that%20is%20just%20not%20viable%2C%20financially%20or%20otherwise.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20why%20wasn't%20the%20ICC%20more%20proactive%20in%20ensuring%20that%20the%20PCB%20are%20fine%20with%20a%20hybrid%20model%2C%20right%20from%20the%20very%20beginning%3F%20Surely%2C%20they%20couldn't%20have%20believed%20that%20the%20Indian%20team%20would%20be%20given%20a%20prompt%20green%20signal%20to%20travel%20to%20Pakistan%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20is%2C%20a%20global%20cricket%20tournament%20without%20India%20is%20unfathomable.%20Indian%20cricket%20brings%20in%20the%20maximum%20amount%20of%20money%20in%20commercial%20revenue%20for%20the%20ICC.%20The%20new%20ICC%20revenue%20distribution%20model%20that%20was%20cleared%20by%20the%20ICC%20board%20in%20July%20last%20year%20approved%20the%20formula%20that%20sees%20the%20BCCI%20take%20almost%2039%25%20of%20the%20ICC's%20net%20surplus%20annual%20earnings%20of%20around%20%24600%20million.%20No%20other%20full-member%20board%20has%20even%20a%20double-digit%20percentage%20share.%20In%20the%202024-2027%20commercial%20cycle%2C%20the%20BCCI%20is%20earning%20about%20%24230%20million%20annually%20from%20the%20ICC's%20global%20earnings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Mammoth%20Industry%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMedia%20rights%20sales%20and%20viewership%20are%20two%20big%20parameters%20that%20were%20integral%20in%20this%20formula.%20It's%20no%20secret%20that%20Indian%20cricket%2C%20and%20also%20cricket%20in%20India%2C%20contributes%20the%20most%20to%20the%20global%20cricket%20economy.%20Though%20the%20exact%20details%20were%20not%20disclosed%2C%20reports%20claimed%20that%20Star%20India%20acquired%20ICC's%20India%20media%20rights%20for%20the%202015-2023%20cycle%20for%20about%20%241.8-2%20billion.%20According%20to%20the%20ICC%2C%20the%20deal%20was%20%E2%80%9Csignificantly%20in%20excess%20of%20the%20ICC's%20previous%20commercial%20deals.%E2%80%9D%20As%20per%20their%20financial%20statement%20and%20media%20reports%2C%20the%20ICC%20earned%20a%20record%20%24719%20million%20from%20the%202023%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20held%20in%20India.%20That's%20about%20%24162%20million%20more%20than%20what%20they%20earned%20from%20the%202019%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20in%20England.%20The%202023%20edition%20was%20also%20the%20largest%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20overall%20viewership%20and%20spectator%20turnout.%20According%20to%20an%20ICC%20release%2C%20it%20recorded%20over%20a%20trillion%20viewing%20minutes%E2%80%94a%2038%25%20jump%20from%20the%20last%20edition%20in%20India%20in%202011.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20same%20release%2C%20the%20final%20between%20India%20and%20Australia%20was%20the%20most%20watched%20ICC%20match%20ever%2C%20with%2087.6%20billion%20live%20viewing%20minutes%20recorded%20globally.%20As%20many%20as%2020%20broadcast%20partners%20across%20209%20territories%20beamed%20the%20games%20worldwide.%20Even%20when%20a%20tournament%20is%20not%20being%20played%20in%20India%2C%20the%20country%20matches%20attract%20the%20maximum%20eyeballs.%20According%20to%20media%20reports%2C%20the%20India%20vs%20South%20Africa%202024%20men's%20T20%20World%20Cup%20final%20match%20recorded%20a%20peak%20concurrent%20viewership%20of%20almost%205.3%20crore%20on%20the%20Indian%20host%20broadcaster's%20OTT%20platform.%20There's%20a%20reason%20why%20India's%20matches%20at%20global%20tournaments%20are%20almost%20always%20scheduled%20for%20Sundays%20or%20holidays.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20India%20can%20afford%20not%20to%20play%20in%20Pakistan.%20It%20would%20just%20be%20prudent%20for%20the%20ICC%20and%20the%20PCB%20to%20discuss%20a%20hybrid%20model%20for%20the%20India%20matches%2C%20just%20like%20it%20was%20organised%20for%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESafety%20Is%20Foremost%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20so%2C%20there's%20no%20doubt%20that%20it's%20not%20easy%20being%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Pakistan%20cricket%20administration%2C%20or%20even%20a%20Pakistan%20fan%20who%20wants%20to%20see%20an%20India%20vs%20Pakistan%20clash%20in%20her%20or%20his%20country.%20The%20PCB%20desperately%20wants%20Indian%20cricketers%20to%20play%20on%20their%20soil.%20Fans%20in%20Pakistan%20are%20desperate%20to%20see%20and%20even%20cheer%20the%20likes%20of%20Virat%2C%20Rohit%2C%20Bumrah%2C%20Pant%20and%20others%20from%20stands%20in%20Pakistani%20stadiums.%20Despite%20their%20rather%20lop-sided%20rivalry%20in%20recent%20times%2C%20India%20vs%20Pakistan%20is%20still%20very%20much%20an%20emotional%20clash%2C%20for%20fans%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20border.%20But%20the%20safety%20and%20security%20of%20its%20citizens%20is%20the%20highest%20priority%20for%20any%20government%2C%20despite%20whatever%20%E2%80%98security%20and%20safety%20experts'%20might%20conclude%20after%20visiting%20empty%20stadiums%20and%20travelling%20on%20roads%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20venue%20on%20non-match%20days.%20Neither%20the%20PCB%20nor%20the%20ICC%20can%20realistically%20convince%20the%20Indian%20government%20to%20allow%20the%20cricket%20team%20to%20travel%20to%20Pakistan.%20The%20writing%20has%20been%20firmly%20on%20the%20wall%20for%20a%20long%20time%20now.%20A%20plan%20to%20work%20on%20a%20hybrid%20model%20should%20have%20been%20drawn%20up%20a%20long%20time%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BCCI%20is%20not%20arbitrarily%20taking%20the%20decision%20not%20to%20play%20in%20Pakistan.%20It's%20the%20Indian%20government%20that%20has%20the%20final%20say.%20The%20Indian%20men's%20blind%20cricket%20team%20obtained%20a%20no-objection%20certificate%20from%20the%20sports%20ministry%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20T20%20Blind%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20scheduled%20to%20be%20held%20from%20November%2022%20to%20December%203.%20But%20they%20were%20not%20given%20MEA%20clearance%20and%20have%20subsequently%20withdrawn%20from%20the%20tournament.%20The%20same%20decision%20was%20taken%20for%20the%20Indian%20kabaddi%20team%2C%20which%20was%20scheduled%20to%20play%20three%20friendly%20games%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20this%20month.%20Pakistan%20is%20where%20the%20Sri%20Lankan%20men's%20cricket%20team%20bus%20was%20shot%20at%20by%2012%20gunmen%20near%20the%20Gaddafi%20stadium%20in%20Lahore%20in%202009.%20Sure%2C%20other%20countries%20are%20touring%20Pakistan%20again%20to%20play%20cricket%2C%20but%20India's%20equation%20is%20different.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Standoff%20Continues%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%20the%20ninth%20of%20this%20month%2C%20the%20BCCI%20informed%20the%20ICC%20that%20the%20Indian%20team%20will%20not%20get%20government%20clearance%20to%20travel%20to%20Pakistan%20for%20the%20Champions%20Trophy.%20The%20final%20schedule%20for%20the%20tournament%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20announced%20by%20November%2020%2C%20but%20it%20wasn't%2C%20and%20reports%20from%20Pakistan%20indicate%20that%20the%20delay%20is%20due%20to%20the%20ICC's%20inability%20to%20convince%20the%20PCB%20to%20adopt%20a%20hybrid%20model.%20Some%20reports%20claim%20that%20the%20broadcasters%20and%20advertisers%20in%20Pakistan%20are%20putting%20pressure%20on%20their%20board%2C%20demanding%20that%20India%20play%20their%20matches%20only%20on%20Pakistan%20soil.%20PCB%20Chairman%20Mohsin%20Naqvi%20has%20confirmed%20that%20they%20are%20%E2%80%98just%20talking%20to%20the%20ICC'.%20None%20of%20this%20is%20surprising.%20And%20with%20just%20around%20three%20months%20to%20go%20now%20for%20the%20tournament%2C%20it%20won't%20be%20surprising%20if%20and%20when%20the%20PCB%20agrees%20to%20a%20hybrid%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20were%20awarded%20the%20hosting%20rights%20for%20next%20year's%20Champions%20Trophy%20exactly%20three%20years%20ago.%20That's%20how%20much%20time%20the%20ICC%20has%20had%20to%20ensure%20two%20very%20important%20things%E2%80%94Pakistan%20retaining%20hosting%20rights%20and%20India's%20participation%20in%20the%20tournament.%20Now%2C%20with%20the%20clock%20ticking%2C%20and%20the%20PCB%20digging%20in%20its%20heels%2C%20they%20find%20themselves%20in%20an%20almost%20impossible%20situation%20of%20their%20own%20making.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20author%20is%20a%20former%20sports%20editor%20and%20primetime%20sports%20news%20anchor.%20He%20is%20currently%20a%20columnist%2C%20features%20writer%20and%20stage%20actor)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732279980000%2C%22visual%22