ot%3B%20said%20Saibal%20Chakraborty%2C%20India%20Leader%2C%20Technology%20and%20Digital%20Advantage%20Practice%2C%20BCG.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20ranks%20second%20globally%20in%20AI%20specialists%20and%203rd%20in%20research%20publications%2C%20with%20a%20strong%20base%20in%20AI-related%20patents%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20further%20showed%20that%20AI%20exposure%20spans%20several%20key%20sectors%20in%20India.%20Business%20services%20account%20for%2016%20per%20cent%20of%20GDP%20and%20have%20significant%20AI%20exposure%2C%20with%20potential%20improvements%20in%20administrative%20efficiency%20for%20government%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERetail%20and%20wholesale%20make%20up%2010%20per%20cent%20of%20GDP%2C%20where%20AI%20could%20streamline%20public%20distribution%20and%20supply%20chain%20management%2C%20reducing%20wastage.%20Public%20services%20represent%206%20per%20cent%20of%20GDP%2C%20with%20opportunities%20for%20AI%20to%20enhance%20service%20delivery%20and%20emergency%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgriculture%2C%20forestry%2C%20and%20fisheries%20contribute%2017%20per%20cent%20of%20GDP%20and%20could%20use%20AI%20in%20precision%20farming%20and%20risk%20assessment%20to%20boost%20productivity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20construction%20sector%2C%20at%208%20per%20cent%20of%20GDP%2C%20can%20utilise%20AI%20for%20infrastructure%20planning%20and%20asset%20maintenance.%20Arts%2C%20recreation%2C%20and%20personal%20services%2C%20also%20at%208%20per%20cent%2C%20could%20benefit%20from%20AI%20in%20managing%20public%20facilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRealising%20this%20potential%20requires%20a%20multi-faceted%20approach%3A%20strengthening%20infrastructure%2C%20enhancing%20AI%20research%20capabilities%2C%20and%20expanding%20workforce%20training.%20Investments%20in%20research%20hubs%2C%20cloud%20capabilities%2C%20and%20data%20systems%20are%20critical%2C%20alongside%20efforts%20to%20expand%20AI%20education%20in%20rural%20area