travel%20for%20women%2C%20pilgrimage%20scheme%20for%20the%20elderly%20and%20monthly%20Rs%201%2C000%20assistance%20for%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20said%20AAP%20workers%20will%20ask%20the%20voters%20what%20the%20BJP%20has%20done%20for%20Delhi%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years%20since%20%26quot%3Bthe%20national%20capital%20is%20a%20half-state%20and%20the%20central%20government%20has%20as%20many%20powers%20as%20we%20do%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThe%20BJP%20is%20in%20power%20in%2020%20states%20and%20not%20even%20in%20a%20single%20state%20do%20they%20provide%20any%20of%20these%20free%20'revdis'.%20This%20is%20because%20they%20don't%20have%20the%20intention.%20Only%20AAP%20knows%20how%20to%20provide%20these%20facilities%2C%26quot%3B%20Kejriwal%20said%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20only%20halted%20his%20government's%20works.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20also%20accused%20Union%20Ministers%20Amit%20Shah%20and%20Hardeep%20Puri%20of%20making%20false%20promises%20to%20the%20Purvanchali%20community%20during%20the%20last%20elections.%20%26quot%3BThey%20promised%20proper%20registrations%20for%20unauthorised%20colonies%20but%20haven't%20completed%20even%20one%20in%20five%20years.%20In%20contrast%2C%20we've%20given%20dignity%20to%20the%20lives%20of%20Purvanchal%20residents%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20has%20named%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faap-names-11-candidates-in-first-list-for-delhi-polls-due-by-february-7070272%3Fpfrom%3Ddesktop-https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fcoronavirus%2Findia-covid-19-tracker%5C%22%3E11%20candidates%20for%20the%20Delhi%20Assembly%20elections%3C%2Fa%3E.%20While%20Brahma%20Singh%20Tanwar%20will%20contest%20from%20Chhatarpur%2C%20Anil%20Jha%20will%20be%20AAP%20candidate%20from%20Kiradi.%20Deepak%20Singhla%20will%20contest%20in%20Vishwas%20Nagar%20and%20Sarita%20Singh%20in%20Rohtas%20Nagar.%20BB%20Tyagi%20has%20been%20named%20AAP%20candidate%20in%20Laxmi%20Nag