0the%20stigma%20of%20a%20cancer%20diagnosis.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20heartbreaking%20that%20families%20worry%20more%20about%20societal%20opinions%20than%20the%20patient%E2%80%99s%20well-being%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CHealthcare%20professionals%20should%20also%20encourage%20counselling%20for%20patients%20with%20terminal%20illness.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECaregivers%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F332931%2Fnamarita-kathait-started-the-listening-circles-promote-mental-health%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprimarily%20require%20therapy%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20their%20journey%20is%20as%20challenging%20as%20the%20one%20with%20a%20physical%20illness.%20The%20pressure%20of%20providing%20the%20proper%20care%20for%20the%20patient%2C%20financial%20struggle%2C%20etc%2C%20also%20takes%20a%20toll%20on%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20620px)%20100vw%2C%20620px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Ffile-2_11zon-1732189289.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22620%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Alpa%20in%20conversation%20with%20a%20cancer%20patient.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Ffile-2_11zon-1732189289.jpg%20620w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Ffile-2_11zon-1732189289-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Ffile-2_11zon-1732189289-500x500.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Ffile-2_11zon-1732189289-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Ffile-2_11zon-1732189289-600x600.jpg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com