ived%2C%20owing%20to%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20family%20home%20in%20Kangra.%20It%20was%20during%20one%20such%20trip%20that%20Deepak%20had%20his%20moment%20of%20catharsis.%20%E2%80%9CI%20decided%20to%20build%20a%20home.%20A%20sustainable%20one%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20reasons%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20grew%20up%20on%20tea%20estates%2C%20and%20have%20always%20enjoyed%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F373216%2Faashraya-on-the-ganga-rishikesh-depi-chaudhry-sustainable-eco-friendly-homestays-uttarakhand%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elarge%20spaces%20and%20big%20homes%3C%2Fa%3E.%20For%20many%20years%2C%20this%20was%20missing%20for%20us%20at%20Wah%20Tea%20Estate.%20Spending%20time%20in%20the%20city%20meant%20having%20to%20deal%20with%20pollution%20and%20other%20carcinogenic%20substances.%20I%20felt%20it%20was%20time%20to%20correct%20that.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20started%20as%20an%20idea%20for%20a%20single%20cottage%20soon%20matured%20into%20a%20homestay%20with%20three.%20%E2%80%9CDad%20got%20a%20tad%20bit%20excited%2C%E2%80%9D%20Deepak%E2%80%99s%20daughter-in-law%2C%20Upasana%2C%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FLodge-at-Wah-sustainable-travel-9-1732100160.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20brews%20found%20at%20The%20Lodge%20at%20Wah%20are%20prepared%20from%20tea%20leaves%20that%20are%20grown%20using%20organic%20methods%20of%20farming%20%5Cn%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FLodge-at-Wah-sustainable-travel-9-1732100160.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2