rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F307729%2Fclimate-resilient-goat-shed-model-by-seeds-india-prevents-livestock-loss-during-flood-earthquake-bihar%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efloods%20in%20Bihar%3C%2Fa%3E%20often%20wiped%20out%20crops%2C%20leaving%20farmers%20with%20no%20returns.%20Meanwhile%2C%20rice%20farming%2C%20the%20region%E2%80%99s%20fallback%20option%2C%20offered%20meagre%20profits%20and%20an%20unsustainable%20livelihood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20vision%20to%20change%20the%20face%20of%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%3C%2Fem%3E%20cultivation%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Manoj%20Kumar%20spent%20a%20decade%20researching%20ways%20to%20make%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%20%3C%2Fem%3Efarming%20more%20efficient%2C%20sustainable%2C%20and%20less%20labour-intensive.%20One%20of%20his%20breakthroughs%20was%20proving%20that%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%3C%2Fem%3E%20could%20thrive%20in%20water%20as%20shallow%20as%2030%20cm%2C%20contrary%20to%20the%20traditional%20belief%20that%20five%20to%20six%20feet%20was%20necessary.%20This%20discovery%20allowed%20farmers%20to%20grow%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%3C%2Fem%3E%20like%20any%20other%20crop%20in%20fields%2C%20reducing%20dependence%20on%20deep%2C%20flood-prone%20ponds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Kumar%20also%20developed%20a%20high-yielding%20variety%20of%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%3C%2Fem%3E%20called%20%E2%80%98Swarna%20Vaidehi%3Cem%3E%E2%80%99%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20a%20high-yielding%20variety%20of%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%3C%2Fem%3E.%20This%20variety%20adapted%20well%20to%20local%20conditions%20and%20significantly%20increased%20productivity.%20Additionally%2C%20techniques%20like%20nursery%20raising%20(growing%20seedlings%20separately%20before%20transplanting)%20and%20line%20planting%20(organised%20sowing%20in%20rows)%20were%20introduced.%20These%20methods%20reduced%20seed%20requirements%20and%20improved%20yields%2C%20making%20farming%20more%20efficient.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EOvercoming%20the%20flood%20challenge%20with%20innovative%20net%20fencing%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFloods%20have%20long%20been%20a%20major%20threat%20to%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%3C%2Fem%3E%20farming%2C%20often%20destroying%20entire%20crops.%20Dr%20Kumar%20tackled%20this%20issue%20by%20introducing%20net%20fencing%2C%20a%20simple%20yet%20effective%20solution.%20It%20involves%20installing%20mesh%20barriers%20around%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%20%3C%2Fem%3Efields%20to%20protect%20crops%20from%20being%20washed%20away%20by%20floodwaters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%202294px)%20100vw%2C%202294px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Ffox2_11zon-1732293353.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222294%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Floods%20threaten%20makhana%20crops%2C%20but%20innovative%20solutions%20like%20net%20fencing%20provide%20protection%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Ffox2_11zon-1732293353.jpg%202294w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Ffox2_11zon-1732293353-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Ffox2_11zon-1732293353-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Ffox2_11zon-1732293353-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Ffox2_11zon-1732293353-1536x1152.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Ffox2_11zon-1732293353-2048x1536.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Ffox2_11zon-1732293353-1200x900.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Ffox2_11zon-1732293353-800x600.jpg%2080